 - handle non-keyword words (C#) -- example: @if @switch
 - set the parent on 'do' braces
 - handle C# #region preprocessor stuff
 - partially implement align on tabstop
 - fix virtual brace spacing (no more "else return;" => "elsereturn;")
 - add some more tests

